your design time in half\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eWhile there’s a lot you can do with the free version, you can also \u003ca href=\"http://www.makeuseof.com/favorite-canva-pro-features/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003esubscribe to a trial run of Canva Pro\u003c/a\u003e if you’d like to take advantage of the premium features. You can use the free trial for up to 30 days, which is plenty of time to design a Valentine’s Day card that checks all the boxes.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"greetings-island\"\u003e\n            \u003cspan\u003e3 \u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003cspan\u003e\n                            \u003ca href=\"https://www.greetingsisland.com/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eGreetings Island\u003c/a\u003e\n                    \u003c/span\u003e\n       \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                            \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.makeuseofimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/screenshot-2025-02-02-at-1-24-31-am.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.mak